column1: IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0

IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thb_d is MF 0 AND ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 2 AND ccr_pt_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 1
